resources.string:
Hello!

This is an unnofical Scheduleman app for CMU students.

You can type/paste in a full URL
(https://scheduleman.org/schedules/AtoAAW0Vgk)

or just the identifier at the end 
(AtoAAW0Vgk).

These identifiers are case insensitive. 

There is currently wonky support with Sunday classes. Sorry Qatar!

Problems or suggestions, send over to schedulemanApp@gmail.com, with offending schedule when possible.
